    "title": "Setting up the hardware",
    "content": "The following table shows the target hardware for the application projects. | Project Name | Board | . | sam_a7g5_ek.X | SAMA7G5 Evaluation Kit | . Setting up SAMA7G5 Evaluation Kit . Setting up the board . | Connect a 5V power supply to the board. This can be either of the following: . | A USB cable connected between “USBA” (J7) connector on the board and USB host port on PC | A 5V DC adapter connected to “5V DC IN” (J1) connector on board | . | Connect the Debug USB port (J24) on the board to the computer using a micro USB cable | Remove DISABLE_BOOT (J21) jumper as this is required for using SW4 switch | . ",
