    "content": "The following table shows the target hardware for the application projects. | Project Name | Board | . | sam_a7g5_ek.X | SAMA7G5 Evaluation Kit | . Setting up SAMA7G5 Evaluation Kit . Addtional hardware required . | SD Card with FAT32 file system | . Setting up the SD Card . | Download harmony MPU bootstrap loader from this location | Copy the downloaded boot loader binary( boot.bin) onto the SD card | . Setting up the board . | SDMMC slot used for bootloading the application is SDMMC0 (J4) | Connect a 5V power supply to the board. This can be either of the following: . | A USB cable connected between “USBA” (J7) connector on the board and USB host port on PC | A 5V DC adapter connected to “5V DC IN” (J1) connector on board | . | Connect the Debug USB port (J24) on the board to the computer using a micro USB cable | Short TIOA pin of TC0, Channel 2 with TIOA pin of TC2, Channel 0 | . ",
